data.description: Welcome to this updated and well maintained 4 bedroom home just moments from all the downtown happenings of Madison County. This property features a great over sized detached 3 car garage, a perfectly sized back yard, and a home boasting over 1,800 sq ft. Inside you will find a finished basement with a solid foundation, updated electrical throughout, 4th bedroom, 3rd full bath, open space perfect for a play area or smaller in home theater, tankless water heater, and updated furnace. You will find the open concept main level perfect for a family who loves to entertain; with 2 bedrooms, 2nd full bath, laundry room, and a beautifully updated kitchen that has room for all the cooking supplies one could ask for. Upstairs, on the 2nd floor a private master suite with a full bath and plenty of space for your own get away office, or sitting area awaits. Call your favorite REALTOR today to call this maintenance free home yours! 2023-10-20
